Union of Theoretical Grammarians in Cambridge. B.S. Meniscus Films, Ltd. Documentary cast;  mm.;  minutes; color; silent w/ heavy use of computerized distortion in facial close-ups. Documentary and closed-caption interviews with participants in the public Steven Pinker-Avril M. Incandenza debate on the political implications of prescriptive grammar during the infamous Militant Grammarians of Massachusetts convention credited with helping incite the M.I.T. language riots of B.S. . UNRELEASED DUE TO LITIGATION
